# NASA API Key — get yours free at https://api.nasa.gov/
# Replace DEMO_KEY in index.html with your personal key to avoid rate limits.
# Your key goes here in index.html as:
#   const NASA_API_KEY = "YOUR_KEY_HERE";
#
# IMPORTANT: Never commit a real key. This .env.example is safe to commit.
# Your .gitignore already excludes all .env files except this one.
NASA_API_KEY="YOUR_NASA_KEY_HERE"
